title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Apr 25 2022

description:
Dr. Osterholm on masks and condoms. Mary Katharine Ham and Bill Maher mock crazy covid stuff. Trump Takes it to Democrats at Ohio rally. Sen. Rand Paul joins Clay and Buck to discuss mask mandate, predicts Hunter Biden indictment, his view on Elon Musk buying Twitter. C&B discuss the Hunter Biden case.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
